        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-2d1e145d-fbf1-4216-ab02-4bcb5a4912c3">
                The Parliamentary and Financial Secretary to the Admiralty (Mr. James Callaghan)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2d1e145d-fbf1-4216-ab02-4bcb5a4912c3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-04-19/debates/08d3816d-82ee-4c81-8e15-5a236c0bd675/NorthAtlantic(SupremeCommander)#contribution-2d1e145d-fbf1-4216-ab02-4bcb5a4912c3">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">It may be quite true that the Americans have a much larger material reserve, but I suggest to the right hon. Gentleman that they do not possess a proportionately larger material reserve than we have, compared with their active fleet.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2d1e145d-fbf1-4216-ab02-4bcb5a4912c3" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-04-19/debates/08d3816d-82ee-4c81-8e15-5a236c0bd675/NorthAtlantic(SupremeCommander)#contribution-2d1e145d-fbf1-4216-ab02-4bcb5a4912c3">
