    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I think we do not do that here.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-8468f5ee-cee6-482f-9ed9-845be62d9a61" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
