                Mr. Shinwell
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-aa3c60a5-5f33-476d-a9f3-a5ed3265d84f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
