                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-57a0d8d9-a85c-47e7-86a0-371db471e433" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
