            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-478ebba6-ecc4-4de9-b9fb-c22f3eb02a3b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1951-04-19/debates/08d3816d-82ee-4c81-8e15-5a236c0bd675/NorthAtlantic(SupremeCommander)#contribution-478ebba6-ecc4-4de9-b9fb-c22f3eb02a3b">
